{"ts": "2026-06-08T04:01:29.592538+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "successfully downloaded text file (SHA: 88604af8e984fb05b03e230f221e0374071d014f)", "id": "lc_ab5c70a0-cc5c-40fa-9626-d55e93b9e1a3"}, {"type": "text", "text": "# vue-admin-template\n\n> 这是一个极简的 vue admin 管理后台。它只包含了 Element UI & axios & iconfont & permission control & lint，这些搭建后台必要的东西。\n\n[github 线上地址](https://HaitaoWang555.github.io/vue3-admin-template)\n[gitee 线上地址](http://wanghaitao555.gitee.io/vue3-admin-template)\n\n**Pro 线上地址:** https://haitaowang555.github.io/vue3-admin-pro\n\n\n**Pro 线上地址:** https://wanghaitao555.gitee.io/vue3-admin-pro\n\n## Build Setup\n\n```bash\n# 克隆项目\ngit clone https://github.com/HaitaoWang555/vue3-admin-template.git\n\n# 进入项目目录\ncd vue3-admin-template\n\n# 安装pnpm\nnpm i -g pnpm\n\n# 安装依赖\npnpm install\n\n# 启动服务\npnpm dev\n```\n\n浏览器访问 [http://localhost:9528](http://localhost:9528)\n\n## 发布\n\n```bash\n# 构建测试环境\npnpm build:stage\n\n# 构建生产环境\npnpm build:prod\n```\n\n## 其它\n\n```bash\n# 预览发布环境效果\npnpm preview\n\n# 预览发布环境效果 + 静态资源分析\npnpm preview -- --report\n\n# 代码格式检查\npnpm lint\n\n# 代码格式检查并自动修复\npnpm lint -- --fix\n```\n\n## License\n\n[MIT](https://github.com/HaitaoWang555/vue3-admin-template/blob/master/LICENSE) license.\n\nCopyright (c) 2017-present HaitaoWang555\n", "id": "lc_13ec3f33-80ca-4b3b-ab1f-2f4d89f04f47"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": "get_file_contents", "id": "324c8c3b-2f4f-4654-8610-49d5c049f952", "tool_call_id": "call_00_4MyG3JnydpyOuoU6TXwY4616", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}]}}}
{"ts": "2026-06-08T04:01:44.066317+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "Based on the repository contents, here is the relevant information:\n\n## Production Build\n\nThe **admin app** (a Vue 3 + Element Plus admin template) uses **pnpm** as its package manager. The production build command is:\n\n```bash\npnpm build:prod\n```\n\nThis runs `vue-cli-service build` in production mode, using the settings from `.env.production` (which sets `NODE_ENV=production` and `VUE_APP_BASE_API=/prod-api`). The built output is placed in the `dist/` directory.", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 842, "prompt_tokens": 11903, "total_tokens": 12745, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": null, "reasoning_tokens": 723, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": null, "cached_tokens": 11392}, "prompt_cache_hit_tokens": 11392, "prompt_cache_miss_tokens": 511}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "deepseek-v4-pro", "system_fingerprint": "fp_9954b31ca7_prod0820_fp8_kvcache_20260402", "id": "3854e97f-84f2-4280-a287-2c544ecd9d83", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea564-87f9-7670-b381-842bc8115240-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 11903, "output_tokens": 842, "total_tokens": 12745, "input_token_details": {"cache_read": 11392}, "output_token_details": {"reasoning": 723}}}}]}}}
